<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Dashboard de Usuario</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen p-4">
    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full max-w-md text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">¡Bienvenido{{#userName}}, {{userName}}{{/userName}}!</h1>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">Es un placer tenerte de vuelta.</p>

        
        <div class="space-y-4">
            <a href="/profile/view"
               class="inline-block w-full bg-blue-600 text-white py-3 px-6 rounded-md hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:ring-offset-2 text-lg font-medium transition duration-150 ease-in-out">
                Ir a mi Perfil
            </a>
            <a href="/logout"
               class="inline-block w-full bg-gray-500 text-white py-3 px-6 rounded-md hover:bg-gray-600 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gray-400 focus:ring-offset-2 text-lg font-medium transition duration-150 ease-in-out">
                Cerrar Sesión
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center mt-6">
            <a href="/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline text-sm">Volver al inicio</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>